defaultWhat Helen says is exactly right.  There are so many aims attached to open data.  
defaultThere are economic aims about hunting down waste and encouraging use by business.  
defaultThere are political aims about participation and transparency.  
defaultThere are social aims about empowering communities.  There are so many
